  "body": "## Install\n\n### macOS (Apple Silicon)\n```sh\ncurl -Lo agtop https://github.com/collectiveai-team/rust-agtop/releases/download/v0.5.0/agtop-aarch64-apple-darwin\nchmod +x agtop && sudo mv agtop /usr/local/bin/\n```\n\n### macOS (Intel)\n```sh\ncurl -Lo agtop https://github.com/collectiveai-team/rust-agtop/releases/download/v0.5.0/agtop-x86_64-apple-darwin\nchmod +x agtop && sudo mv agtop /usr/local/bin/\n```\n\n### Linux x86_64\n```sh\ncurl -Lo agtop https://github.com/collectiveai-team/rust-agtop/releases/download/v0.5.0/agtop-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\nchmod +x agtop && sudo mv agtop /usr/local/bin/\n```\n\n### From source (cargo)\n```sh\ncargo install --git https://github.com/collectiveai-team/rust-agtop --tag v0.5.0 agtop-cli\n```\n\n\n## What's Changed\n* feat: streaming startup with persistent SQLite cache by @jedzill4 in https://github.com/collectiveai-team/rust-agtop/pull/35\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/collectiveai-team/rust-agtop/compare/v0.4.4...v0.5.0",
